Copy the appropriate script files into your openidm/script folder.
Copy the appropriate conf files into your openidm/conf folder.

Set the appropriate permissions for acccess to the endpoint/childManager endpoint in the script/access.js file.

The managed.json file already contains the necessary managed objects and on hook placements.

Edit the script files if you need to change the flow or logic.

To create a child send a JSON payload to ../openidm/endpoint/childManager?action=child whilst logged in as a parent - this is important.  Being logged in as openidm-admin will fail.
